Cost-effectiveness of the Self-Help Plus Intervention for Adult Syrian Refugees 
Hosted in Turkey.

Park AL(1)(2), Waldmann T(1), Kösters M(1), Tedeschi F(3), Nosè M(3), Ostuzzi 
G(3), Purgato M(3), Turrini G(3), Välimäki M(4)(5), Lantta T(4), Anttila M(4), 
