Author information:
(1)Department of Psychiatry and Psychotherapy II, University of Ulm and BKH 
Günzburg, Ulm, Germany.
(2)Care Policy and Evaluation Centre, Department of Health Policy, London School 
of Economics and Political Science, London, United Kingdom.
(3)WHO Collaborating Centre for Research and Training in Mental Health and 
